org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.ucm.profile.UCMProfile.ucm_interactions

Interface ConnectorDefinition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IConfigurable, IInteractionDefinition, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConnectorDefinitionImpl

    public interface ConnectorDefinition
extends IInteractionDefinition, IConfigurable
    A representation of the model object 'Connector Definition'. ConnectorDefinition's ports (ownedPorts) must be ConnectorPorts To extends anConnectorDefinition, use the redefinedClassifier association form metaclass. Item bindings must be added in the metaclass component properties (ownedAttributes) verify that connectorDefinition realizes InteractionPattern
    See Also:
